@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ywpaje(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.18 - v0)
    tmp = (tmp - wp.exp((v0 + 0.13 + v0 + 0.27)))
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.48) + (v2 + 0.80 - v2 + 0.41)) + ((tmp + 0.12 * v1 + 0.61) - tmp))
    v1 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.92) * 0.65) + wp.exp(v2))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp))
    v1 = 0.13
    data[tid] = v0
